<chl><title xml:id="id_pn6k">Present Offer Business Interaction</title>
<chl><title xml:id="id_9h2w">CRUD Operations</title>
<chl><title xml:id="id_338m">Create</title>
<chl><title xml:id="id_6mal">Operations</title>
<p>The following HTTP methods and URIs are applicable to perform the
operation:</p>
<table>
<caption>Create Service Operation</caption>
<tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="0.82*"/><colspec
colname="col2" colwidth="0.55*"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.63*"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="top"><tp>Description</tp>
</entry>
<entry valign="top"><tp>Method</tp>
</entry>
<entry valign="top"><tp>URI</tp>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody><row>
<entry><tp>This operation creates and updates the shopping cart.</tp>
</entry>
<entry><tp><resource-id>POST</resource-id></tp>
</entry>
<entry><tp><resource-id>&lt;scheme>://&lt;host>[:&lt;port>]/cpi/orchestration/v1/bi/&lt;presentOfferBiId></resource-id
></tp>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<p>The following use cases are available when creating a Present Offer
Business Interaction: </p>
<list>
<list-item><p><link linkend="createPOBI">Create Present Offer Business
Interaction</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="addFaF">Create Present Offer Business
Interaction to Add Friends and Family (FaF) List</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link
linkend="CreatePOBItoCreateandValidatecartitemswithContextAttributes"
>Create Present Offer Business Interaction to Create Cart and Validate
Cart Items with Context Attributes</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="CreatePOBIwithProviderPOandContract"
>Create Present Offer Business Interaction with Provider PO for Existing
Contract</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="CreatePOBIwithConsumerPOandContract"
>Create Present Offer Business Interaction with Consumer PO for Existing
Contract</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="createPOBIwithConsumerPO">Create Present
Offer Business Interaction with Consumer PO</link></p>
</list-item>
</list>
<p>The following use cases illustrate the addition of product offer
items to the existing product portfolio of the customer&mdash;also
known as the installed base. </p>
<list>
<list-item><p><link linkend="chBlock-AddDevice">Add a Device in a
Contract</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="addDeviceWithoutContract">Add a Device
without a Contract</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="addPlan">Add a Plan</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="addAddon">Add an Add-on</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="addBundle">Add a Bundle</link></p>
</list-item>
</list>
<p>The following use cases illustrate the exchange of one product
offer for another.</p>
<list>
<list-item><p><link linkend="exchangePOwithPO">Exchange a Source Product
Offer with a Target Product Offer</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="exchangePOwithAddon">Exchange a Product
Offer with an Add-On Product Offer</link></p>
</list-item>
</list>
<p>The following use cases illustrate the exchange of one resource
for another.</p>
<list>
<list-item><p><link linkend="exchangeLogicalwithPlan">Exchange Logical
Resource under a Plan</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="exchangeLogicalStandAlone">Exchange Logical
Resource as Standalone</link></p>
</list-item>
<list-item><p><link linkend="ExchangePhysicalStandAlone">Exchange
Physical Resource as Standalone</link></p>
</list-item>
</list>
</chl>
<chl><title xml:id="id_wz6r">HTTP Headers</title>
<p>Standard and custom HTTP headers are supported. For more information,
refer to <xref linkend="ID9125308171-1"/>.</p>
</chl>
<chl><title xml:id="id_jlsc">Resource Representation</title>
<p>A description of the elements and their structure is contained
in the resource representation.</p>
<titled-block>
<title>Request Resource Representation</title>
</titled-block>
<p>The <resource-id>BusinessInteraction.json</resource-id> requires
a <resource-id>CPI-PresentOfferBI-2.0.0.spec</resource-id> as input.</p>
<titled-block>
<title>Response Resource Representation</title>
</titled-block>
<p>The <resource-id>BusinessInteraction.json</resource-id> conforms
to <resource-id>CPI-PresentOfferBI-2.0.0.spec</resource-id>.</p>
<p>For details, refer to <xref linkend="abc"/>.</p>
</chl>
</chl>
